:wave: _*Buddy’s startup is seeking a freelance content marketer.* Are you the right person? Reach out to *him* at <mailto:leonard@tell.ie|leonard@tell.ie> (not me! I’m just the messenger!)_ 

Over to Leonard…

&gt; We (<https://join.tell.ie/|Tellie>) are looking for a content marketing contractor (min 6 months) or a full-time hire (or contract-to-hire). We are looking for someone with experience in the no-code website building/creator space (doesn’t have to be an exact match).
&gt; 
&gt; You will manage all of our content marketing including: 
&gt; 
&gt; - crafting content for various channels (social, blog, etc)
&gt; - business relations (getting our content on third parties)
&gt; - SEO
&gt; 
&gt; The primary goal is organic custom acquisition -- we want an engine that feeds our top of the funnel. That will change as we get more users, but for now, it’s the primary goal. 
&gt; 
&gt; *Budget Info*
&gt; 
&gt; • Full-time hire: $110k-$150k depending on seniority. Not sure what the contracting rates would be, but we will try our best to be competitive.
&gt; 
&gt; • Our marketing budget is $10k per month and the content marketing budget would come from that
&gt; <http://tell.ie/|Tellie> allows every creator to build a home for your creativity in minutes. It gives the power of a website with the ease of a link-in-bio tool. With Tellie’s novel design, your work stands out on mobile and desktop. Tell stories across formats and platforms, pairing video, audio, text, images, GIFs, shops, links, and more—creating connections never before possible. Drive valuable stats like streams and views while keeping fans in an experience you own. At Tellie, we don’t prioritize meaningless clicks. We help you build direct relationships with your fans. Your site. Your story. With <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GGWiMtIzEKg|Tellie>.
Reach out to: <mailto:leonard@tell.ie|leonard@tell.ie>
